title: Boston-Back Bay-Beacon Street-Fabulous Apt
posting_body: ['This is a one bedroom in the Best Area...', 'Heart Of Back Bay', 'The Apartment has very nice Cabinets..', 'Granite...Fantastic Stainless Steel Appliances...breakfast bar...', 'Nice Bathroom....living room with fireplace...', 'very high cathedral ceilings....', 'Recessed lighting...2 large windows in living room...', 'Bedroom is good size with plenty of closet space and 2 windows ...', 'Nice ceiling fan in bedroom...', 'Nice Residents in Brownstone....Heat & Hot Water are Included...', 'Walk to Shops at Newbury Street or the Charles River...', 'No Management Company, Just an Owner that Cares...No Fees...', 'Great Deal...', 'Off street parking is available for additional fee.']
